These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, water, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, singing, magic-tricks, reading
1. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking juice##7
4. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | water | soy-milk       | almond-milk | juice        |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks  | singing | reading        | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, fish, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo, skiing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the owner of the fish##7
2. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | fish | rat       | pony         | rabbit     |
| Sport   | water-polo   | lacrosse | skiing | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, sports, spy, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, trance, disco, salsa
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of trance and the fan of metal##7
3. the fan of disco is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the fan of metal is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person watching sports movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | family | spy | action  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | metal  | salsa   | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, fishing, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, soccer, biathlon, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's hobby is chess##7
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | gardening | magic-tricks | chess       | fishing |
| Sport   | soccer      | skiing   | biathlon | snowboarding  |

