.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, traveling, baking, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, colombian, italian, mexican
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the mexican is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is chess##7
5. the mexican is on the left of the italian##1
6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | baking | chess   | board-games | traveling |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | colombian | mexican      | italian |

