.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, soy-milk, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, pakistani, turkish, british
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the turkish is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the pakistani is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the british##3
6. the british is somewhere between the russian and the pakistani##7
7. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | fanta | juice      | soy-milk | iced-tea     |
| Nationality   | russian    | british | pakistani   | turkish |

