.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, cranberry, banana, lemon
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, italian, thai
1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the far left or far right##3
4. the thai is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person eating banana##7
5. the italian is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
6. the thai is on the left or right of the italian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | lemon    | mango   | cranberry | banana  |
| Nationality   | egyptian | italian | thai    | indonesian |

