.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, polish, malaysian, british
4 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, mouse, turtle
1. the polish is not the owner of the turtle##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
3. the british is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the malaysian is somewhere between the british and the dutch##7
5. the polish is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | british | malaysian | polish | dutch |
| Pet           | mouse   | turtle    | goat       | ferret  |

