2. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching western movies and the fan of folk##2
6. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of folk and the person watching western movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | adventure | western | disaster   |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | funk      | electronic      | salsa |

