.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, woodworking, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, train, ship, motorbike
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person driving the train##6
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the train##1
6. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | sudoku | rock-climbing | video-games | woodworking |
| Transport   | van   | motorbike      | train        | ship  |

