2. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the fan of soul##7
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan of soul##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | sprite   | lemonade | hot-chocolate | tea   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | soul   | reggae | classical |

