4. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
5. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the police-officer##7
6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the chef##1
7. the electrician is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Job           | police-officer | mechanic  | chef  | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | western | zombie | time-travel   |

