.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, rat, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, tram, airplane
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the owner of the frog##7
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
5. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | frog    | rat | turtle     | guinea-pig |
| Transport   | tram | airplane  | trike | jet-ski |

 